Title: Cecil paper: "Whole-Program Optimization of Object-Oriented Languages"
Body: Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 03:35:54 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Cecil paper: "Whole-Program Optimization of Object-Oriented Languages" Whole-Program Optimization of Object-Oriented Languages Craig Chambers , Jeffrey Dean , and David Grove We describe Vortex, an optimizing compiler intended to produce high-quality code for programs written in a heavily-object-oriented style.
